{"tid":453443,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"鐘意咗個有男朋友嘅女仔","createTime":"2017-10-31T07:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T08:17:31.000Z","uid":61410,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"adfe170659606279d3128018b20db729a9966f1e","tid":453443,"uid":61410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:45:49.000Z","msg":"一直都有同佢傾計<br />\n可能不知不覺間就俾佢嘅性格吸引咗 鐘意咗佢<br />\n但係我一直都接受唔到自己俾綠帽人帶<br />\n除咗text之外就控制自己唔去做其他界線外嘅野 嘗試去當佢只係一個朋友<br />\n但係最近 佢接近分手嘅時候 當我諗住可以重捨鐘意佢嘅感覺嘅時候 又突然間有個男仔出現<br />\n係佢未分手嘅時候就不停咁追求佢<br />\n佢又會同我講返個男仔追佢嘅情況... 而佢對個男仔又有啲意思<br />\n我都唔知應該用咩心態去應佢<br />\n究竟係唔係我太on9 應該一早就試下追佢<br />\n定係由始至終都係我太犯賤..."},{"pid":"957d7c01b7ac4ebe423ebb13dd0dc5b3e747090a","tid":453443,"uid":85751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:50:59.000Z","msg":"兵就兵啦屌，有咩資格俾帽人帶呀on9"},{"pid":"dfc5422a0c56ad7754f2fa735c29b3c54a25a207","tid":453443,"uid":29254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:52:05.000Z","msg":"巴打我同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢家個女仔同埋個個男仔一齊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47baa0f1ba053a38e135a2796f6d62d3fcd14fb7","tid":453443,"uid":48222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"收皮啦你"},{"pid":"d19f400e745afdac47b48bf6b9d80f13c8df9c78","tid":453443,"uid":93764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:17:31.000Z","msg":"放過人喇，人地根本無預過你"}]}